[[File:Postal zone of Taiwan.svg|250px|thumb|Greater postal zones of [[Taiwan]]]] '''[[Postal code]]s''' ({{zh|c=郵遞區號|p=Yóudì qūhào|poj=Iû-tē khu-hō}}) in '''[[Taiwan]]''' is a system of three + two digits used by [[Chunghwa Post]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.post.gov.tw/post/internet/u_english/postal_e.jsp |title=postalservices Zip Code |publisher=Post.gov.tw |date= |accessdate=2010-12-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720081302/http://www.post.gov.tw/post/internet/u_english/postal_e.jsp |archivedate=2011-07-20 |df= }}</ref> There are 368 sets of three-digit codes for [[Township (Taiwan)|townships]], [[County-controlled city|county-controlled cities]], and [[District (Taiwan)|districts]] in [[Taiwan]].
The cities of [[Chiayi]] and [[Hsinchu]] have a single code covering all their districts. The uninhabited Taiwanese-controlled islands in the groups of [[Pratas Islands|Dongsha (Pratas)]] and [[Spratly Islands|Nansha (Spratly)]] each have a single code. The uninhabited [[Senkaku Islands|Diaoyutai (Senkaku)]] (currently controlled by [[Japan]]) have a code, but there are no deliveries.
Omitting the supplementary two digits is ordinarily acceptable, but using a five-digit code will speed the delivery of the mail.
== Large Postal Code Zones == The first digit is for a large postal zone: {|class="wikitable" !First digit!!Cities!!Counties!!Subsidiary islands |- |<center>'''1'''||[[Taipei]]|| || |- |<center>'''2'''||[[New Taipei]], [[Keelung]]||[[Yilan County, Taiwan|Yilan]], [[Matsu Islands|Lienchiang (Matsu)]]|| [[Senkaku Islands|Diaoyutai Islands]] |- |<center>'''3'''||[[Hsinchu]], [[Taoyuan City|Taoyuan]]||[[Hsinchu County|Hsinchu]], [[Miaoli County|Miaoli]] |- |<center>'''4'''||[[Taichung]]|| || |- |<center>'''5'''|| ||[[Changhua County|Changhua]], [[Nantou County|Nantou]]|| |- |<center>'''6'''||[[Chiayi]]||[[Chiayi County|Chiayi]], [[Yunlin County|Yunlin]]|| |- |<center>'''7'''||[[Tainan]]|| || |- |<center>'''8'''||[[Kaohsiung]]||[[Penghu]], [[Kinmen]]||[[Pratas Islands|Dongsha Islands]], [[Spratly Islands|Nansha Islands]] |- |<center>'''9'''|| ||[[Pingtung County|Pingtung]], [[Taitung County|Taitung]], [[Hualien County|Hualien]] |}
