==Notes== Of the disputed territories, it is practically possible to send mail to Dongsha Island within the [[Pratas Islands|Dongsha Islands]] (817) and [[Taiping Island]], the largest island of the [[Spratly Islands]] (819), as those are above sea level and controlled by Taiwan. There is no mail delivery to the [[Senkaku Islands|Diaoyutai Islands]] (290), as they are controlled by Japan and have been uninhabited for many decades.
